  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/75c585e0b6b09ac5bf12bedde9b4665c.poster.avif?t=1734528145\" width=610 height=223 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/75c585e0b6b09ac5bf12bedde9b4665c.webm?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Get Fun and Try Dying! Sit on the couch or play online with your friends (or just some random guys if you're over thirty). Pick the perfect costume for your adorable water dragon, and push your friends out of the burner... Fry yourself instead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/5401d0862af58ad5373292f77ed84a97.poster.avif?t=1734528145\" width=610 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/5401d0862af58ad5373292f77ed84a97.webm?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Friendly fire: OFF, Self fire: ON, and GO!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play Tug-of-Dynamite, feel like a target for knives, and bathe in burning oil,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break the nooses, stick fingers into a socket, extinguish opponents and farm explosive pumpkins,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, jump-jump, juuuuump, run, fly, dive, smear everything in the mud, freeze, push,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and have a fantastic, crazy party together!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/5f07e0cb8689b30940e0b392f8900eff.poster.avif?t=1734528145\" width=610 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/5f07e0cb8689b30940e0b392f8900eff.webm?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/5f07e0cb8689b30940e0b392f8900eff.mp4?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online or prepare a four-seat couch for local multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dozens and dozens of levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of tools to stop your enemies and buff yourself</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a gamepad or keyboard to play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want more levels to play? Use an editor to create, share, and download custom levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No one can call you Feeder in this game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You and your happy three friends are looking for</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So many dumb ways to die!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disclaimers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no singleplayer mode in the game. At least two players are required for the online and local multiplayer modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the local multiplayer mode, a keyboard can be used only by one player. Other players have to use controllers</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/62c400291f9ccdfa4fcef369fc52eb03.poster.avif?t=1734528145\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/62c400291f9ccdfa4fcef369fc52eb03.webm?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/62c400291f9ccdfa4fcef369fc52eb03.mp4?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/75c585e0b6b09ac5bf12bedde9b4665c.poster.avif?t=1734528145\" width=610 height=223 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/75c585e0b6b09ac5bf12bedde9b4665c.webm?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Get Fun and Try Dying! Sit on the couch or play online with your friends (or just some random guys if you're over thirty). Pick the perfect costume for your adorable water dragon, and push your friends out of the burner... Fry yourself instead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/5401d0862af58ad5373292f77ed84a97.poster.avif?t=1734528145\" width=610 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/5401d0862af58ad5373292f77ed84a97.webm?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Friendly fire: OFF, Self fire: ON, and GO!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play Tug-of-Dynamite, feel like a target for knives, and bathe in burning oil,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break the nooses, stick fingers into a socket, extinguish opponents and farm explosive pumpkins,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, jump-jump, juuuuump, run, fly, dive, smear everything in the mud, freeze, push,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and have a fantastic, crazy party together!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/5f07e0cb8689b30940e0b392f8900eff.poster.avif?t=1734528145\" width=610 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/5f07e0cb8689b30940e0b392f8900eff.webm?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/5f07e0cb8689b30940e0b392f8900eff.mp4?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online or prepare a four-seat couch for local multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dozens and dozens of levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of tools to stop your enemies and buff yourself</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a gamepad or keyboard to play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want more levels to play? Use an editor to create, share, and download custom levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No one can call you Feeder in this game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You and your happy three friends are looking for</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So many dumb ways to die!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disclaimers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no singleplayer mode in the game. At least two players are required for the online and local multiplayer modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the local multiplayer mode, a keyboard can be used only by one player. Other players have to use controllers</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/62c400291f9ccdfa4fcef369fc52eb03.poster.avif?t=1734528145\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/62c400291f9ccdfa4fcef369fc52eb03.webm?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2493920/extras/62c400291f9ccdfa4fcef369fc52eb03.mp4?t=1734528145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
